\subsection{Synthesis}

In general, the existence of a non-uniform dual FB having the same number of filters $G_k$'s and upsampling factors $d_k$'s as the non-uniform analysis FB cannot be guaranteed. Therefore, we use three different approaches to compute the action of the AUDlet synthesis FB: 
